cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and entity recognition. It could also belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it involves identifying relevant entities in a document. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves machine learning techniques for entity recognition. It may also fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves supervised learning and feature extraction.
